			<p>Decades ago, when Mumbai did not look beyond Bandra and Chembur, we spotted a barren quarry land in Powai and foresaw the potential of creating a well-planned township in its place.</p>

			<p>We transformed this hillside quarry land into an integrated township of over 250 acres. Today, it is home to a thriving global community, living in harmony with nature.</p>

			<p>Similarly, we expanded Mumbai city's horizon to Thane by developing around 350 acres of land into a thriving global township with world-class amenities.</p>

			<p>In South India, we are recreating the same magic with Hiranandani Parks! We welcome you to become a part of this City changing movement!</p>

			<p>We take pride in creating integrated, self-sustained townships that are adorned with iconic architecture and world-class amenities. Each township is a city in itself with state-of-the-art Business Parks, Hospitals, Malls, Schools and Recreational facilities along with lush sprawling green spaces.</p>

